---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SubscribeForm from '../components/SubscribeForm.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Subscribe for Updates - ByteLite" 
  description="Get exclusive updates on ByteLite Application Demo and Deep Kore Neural Recursion technology. Be first to know about our breakthrough in computational intelligence."
>

  <section class="subscribe-content">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Main Subscription Form -->
      <SubscribeForm variant="hero" />

      <!-- Information Sections -->
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-icon">ðŸ§ </div>
          <h3>Deep Kore Neural Recursion</h3>
          <p>
            Our compression mathematics have revealed unprecedented patterns in recursive information processing, 
            leading to breakthroughs in neural computation that approach true AGI.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-icon">ðŸ”’</div>
          <h3>Controlled Release</h3>
          <p>
            Technical specifications are now classified due to dual-use considerations. 
            Subscribe to receive updates as authorized information becomes available.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-icon">ðŸ“±</div>
          <h3>ByteLite Application Demo</h3>
          <p>
            Experience the compression technology firsthand. Be notified immediately when our 
            demonstration application is ready for public release.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Section -->
      <div class="faq-section">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>Why is the blueprint no longer available?</h4>
          <p>
            Our mathematical framework has implications beyond compression, particularly in achieving 
            true computational intelligence. We're working with appropriate authorities to ensure 
            responsible disclosure while protecting this breakthrough technology.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>What is Deep Kore Neural Recursion?</h4>
          <p>
            It's the application of ByteLite's recursive compression mathematics to neural architectures, 
            enabling information processing densities that approach theoretical limits of computation.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>When will the ByteLite Application Demo be available?</h4>
          <p>
            We're finalizing security protocols and usage restrictions. Subscribe above to be 
            notified the moment it's released. Early access will be limited.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>Will technical details ever be released?</h4>
          <p>
            We're committed to advancing the field while ensuring responsible use. Technical 
            publications will follow appropriate review and clearance processes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Ethics CTA -->
      <div class="ethics-cta">
        <h3>Our Ethical Framework</h3>
        <p>Learn about our commitment to responsible AI development and the principles guiding Deep Kore's emergence.</p>
        <a href="/ethics" class="btn btn-primary">Read the Genesis Manifesto</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .subscribe-content {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-darker);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .info-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .info-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .info-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .info-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .info-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .faq-section {
    margin-top: 6rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .faq-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.4);
    border: 1px solid rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item:hover {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .faq-item h4 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .info-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .faq-section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }

  /* Ethics CTA */
  .ethics-cta {
    margin-top: 6rem;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.05), rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.05));
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.2);
  }

  .ethics-cta h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .ethics-cta p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-bg-dark);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #00A8CC;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
  }

</style>